{"id":1027209,"date":[{"year":1996,"month":2,"day":15}],"page":"12","source":"","region":"","masthead":"笔会","special_issue":"笔会","column":"","genre":"","count":"144","ytitle":"","mtitle":"题画诗二首","ftitle":"","authors":["关山月"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"关山月"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"题咏梅图(注)"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蓝图远景跨世纪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"民丰国泰又报春；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"前事不忘抗战史，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"砚边再探梅精神。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"题绿荫庇清泉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老来梦寐晚晴天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"难得安居乐业年；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"寄意闲情凭秃笔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抒怀绿荫庇清泉。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"注:最近根据毛主席咏梅句再写《一笑暖千家》红梅一幅，用“俏也不争春，只把春来报”的词意歌颂我国跨世纪的蓝图。"}]}